_______________________________________________________________________________
"Alter Aura"        
 
        This allows the psionicist to do just what it says.  The
        psionicist is displayed the alignment choices of demonic, evil,
        nasty, neutral, nice, good, and saintly and can pick which one
        to become.  Of course future actions  will immediately begin to
        alter this.  As the psionicist guild  does not depend on
        alignments at all this is largely a roleplaying power.  However,
        it can be used to simultaneously wield magic items requiring
        wildly different alingments.  Such is the power of the mind.
        It takes a flat 15 sp.
 
SP Cost:  15		Guild Level:  3		Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  paura <saintly/good/nice/neutral/nasty/evil/demonic>
